<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 5 (Marta) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マルタ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Marta</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ふぅ、疲れた……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whew, I'm tired...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お疲れだね、エミル。
どうかしたの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Good work, Emil.
Is something up?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん。
ミラさんに呼び出されてね
今までずっと話し込んでたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. Milla called for me.
We've been talking for a while now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いろいろ質問されて、もうクタクタだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm just worn out from being
asked all kinds of questions.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>えぇぇぇぇぇぇ！！？
ミラがそんなにしつこく
アプローチしてきたの！！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whaaaaaat?!! Milla was that
persistent in approaching you?!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんでそうなるの！？
僕の話聞いてた、マルタ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why did turn out like this?!
Are you even listening to me, Marta?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミルには私がいるのに！
しつこくアプローチしてくるなんて
許せない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil is mine! I can't forgive her for
approaching him so persistently!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ラストバトルよ！
これは女のラストバトルなんだから！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is the last battle!
This now is the last woman's battle!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
